trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> uses an <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> to deserialize an XML document into a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>XML 문서에 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> 를 deserialize 하는 데</xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 사용 하 여</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> collects validation errors and warnings emitted by the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>에 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>.</xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 내보내는 유효성 검사 오류와 경고를 수집 합니다.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>

trans-unit.source: At certain points during deserialization, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> determines whether the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> has encountered any validation errors, and, if it has, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> adds these warnings and errors to ValidationEventArgs and throws a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException>.
trans-unit.target: 역직렬화 하는 동안 특정 지점에서의 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>결정 여부는 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>모든 유효성 검사 오류가 발생 했습니다 고는 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>이러한 경고와 오류 ValidationEventArgs 추가 하 고 <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileDeserializationException> throw</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer> 된 경우</xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfileSerializer>
